mixin Mission()
    section.mission.container.reveal-zoom
        div
            p 🐔 In this fast-paced mini-game, your mission is clear — guide the brave chicken through a fiery dungeon, dodging flames and making it safely to the other side. Every lane you cross increases the excitement, but be careful — one wrong move, and it’s game over!
            p 🔥 With its dynamic challenges and engaging mechanics, Chicken Road offers endless fun and keeps players coming back for more. Think you have what it takes to make it across?
            div.colored
        div.colored
            h2 Chicken Road – Dare to Cross the Flames!
            p Launched on April 4, 2024, Chicken Road quickly became a favorite among players for its simple yet thrilling gameplay. Now featured on some of the most popular gaming platforms through Inout Games' partners, it’s your turn to take on the challenge!
            +Link({
                class: 'btn',
                href: '#game',
                text: 'Join the Game',
            })